This is Perl module TwitterTranslate.

INSTALLATION

Type the following command:

    $ curl -L http://cpanmin.us | perl - TwitterTranslate

Or install cpanm and then run the following command to install
TwitterTranslate:

    $ cpanm TwitterTranslate

If you get an archive of this distribution, unpack it and build it
as per the usual:

    $ tar xzf TwitterTranslate-$version.tar.gz
    $ cd TwitterTranslate-$version
    $ perl Makefile.PL
    $ make && make test

Then install it:

    $ make install

DOCUMENTATION

TwitterTranslate documentation is available as in POD. So you can do:

    $ perldoc TwitterTranslate

to read the documentation online with your favorite pager.

